dan begitu juga saya.

00:33:55.060 --> 00:33:56.120
Setiap kali anda memerlukan bantuan,

00:33:58.220 --> 00:33:59.340
beritahu saya.

00:34:21.740 --> 00:34:22.580
Tuan Muda,

00:34:22.900 --> 00:34:23.940
kita nak pergi mana?

00:34:27.620 --> 00:34:34.620
